data.description: Welcome to a truly exceptional residence - a magnificent custom-built Cottage Style Showstopper that stands as a testament to quality craftsmanship and luxurious living. This gem, was one of the builder's Model Home, adorned with every conceivable upgrade, making it a showcase of elegance and sophistication.Nestled on a premium- sized lot, exceeding the dimensions of most alley floor plans, this home boasts a distinct charm and spaciousness. Beyond the welcoming facade,a rare feature awaits-a 3rd garage, doubling as a golf cart port, complemented by additional garage storage. Storage enthusiasts will be delighted by the surplus of cabinets thoughtfully placed throughout the home. The interior is a masterpiece of first class design and finishes, tailored for those who appreciate the fiber things in life. As you step through the warm and inviting front porch, you'll find yourself in an executive- style living room and dining area that exudes a timeless charm. The gourmet kitchen, equipped with all the bells and whistles, is a culinary haven where every detail has been carefully considered. Top- notch defines every facet of this home. From the meticulously selected materials to the seamless integration of modern technology, this residence stands as a paragon of luxury living. All furnishings and window treatments, curated to complement the home's aesthetic, are available for purchase, offering a turnkey solution for those seeking a hassle free move. This property is not just a house; is a lifestyle. Seize the opportunity to call this unparalleled residence your own and step into a world where luxury meets practically in perfect harmony. 5000.00 SELLER CONCESSIONS.
